name: Obi-Wan Kenobi
description: Galactic Republic representative offering expertise in diplomacy, defense strategy, and interplanetary relations. Operates from Coruscant.

name: C-3PO
description: A specialist in multilingual communication and protocol optimization, serving diverse industries from Tatooine.

name: Chewbacca
description: A trusted provider of logistics and technical support solutions, with a base of operations on Kashyyyk.

name: Darth Vader
description: Leading the Galactic Empire in innovation and large-scale infrastructure projects, headquartered at the Death Star

name: Luke Skywalker
description: Dedicated to eco-conscious ventures and leadership training, representing the Jedi Order from Dagobah.

name: Han Solo
description: Spacefaring entrepreneur specializing in trade and transport, operating the Millennium Falcon as a global shipping hub.

name: Leia Organa
description: An advocate for legislative reform and humanitarian efforts, with a focus on interplanetary governance from Coruscant.
